## Bundled Tools and Their Licences

Silex bundles or depends on the following open-source software:

- **clang/LLVM**: Apache 2.0 with LLVM exceptions
  https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project

- **mold linker**: MIT
  https://github.com/rui314/mold

- **Ninja build system**: Apache 2.0
  https://github.com/ninja-build/ninja

- **sccache**: Apache 2.0
  https://github.com/mozilla/sccache

- **dash shell**: BSD 3-Clause
  https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/utils/dash/dash.git

- **Wolfi Linux**: Apache 2.0
  https://github.com/wolfi-dev

- **tini**: MIT
  https://github.com/krallin/tini

- **zstd**: BSD 3-Clause
  https://github.com/facebook/zstd

- **xxHash**: BSD 2-Clause
  https://github.com/Cyan4973/xxHash

A full licensing audit with exact versions and licence texts will be provided in v0.2.
